# Ziplofy Yellow Color

When the user asks to "use yellow", "yellow color", or "yellow accent", always use the **Ziplofy brand yellow**:

- **Hex**: `#FBBF24`
- **RGB**: `251, 191, 36`
- **CSS variables** (in CustomThemeBuilder.css): `var(--ziplofy-yellow)` and `rgba(var(--ziplofy-yellow-rgb), <alpha>)`

This is the same yellow used on the Preview button hover in the theme builder. Use it for secondary accents, hover states, and highlights.
